@startuml
[*] --> Campaign Created
Campaign Created --> Approved
Approved --> Campaign Activated
Campaign Activated --> Adverts Prepared
Adverts Prepared --> Adverts Approved
Adverts Approved --> Adverts Scheduled
Adverts Scheduled --> Adverts Running
Adverts Running --> Campaign Extended/Adjusted
Campaign Extended/Adjusted --> Adverts Prepared
Adverts Prepared --> Adverts Approved
Adverts Approved --> Adverts Scheduled
Adverts Scheduled --> Adverts Running
Adverts Running --> Campaign Completed
Campaign Completed --> Final Statement Prepared
Final Statement Prepared --> Payment Handled
Payment Handled --> Amount Paid < Required --> Refund Generated
Payment Handled --> Amount Paid > Required --> Balance Settled
Balance Settled --> Full Amount Paid
Full Amount Paid --> Campaign Paid
Campaign Paid --> Campaign Archived
Campaign Archived --> [*]
@enduml
